      "content": "If a massive, world-altering discovery were being concealed, the most critical data to target would indeed be the raw telemetry and signal data, as that is the uninterpreted stream of reality. Gaps in the raw signal data or sudden, inexplicable changes in the telemetry stream would be the most telling indicators of intentional data modification. While processed imagery can be altered, corrupting the foundational, continuous stream of raw sensor data is a far more definitive method of scrubbing evidence.",
